@prefix ex: <http://example.org/artdance/> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

ex:BlogPost a rdfs:Class .
ex:Artist a rdfs:Class .
ex:Century a rdfs:Class .
ex:Theme a rdfs:Class .

ex:mentionsArtist a rdf:Property .
ex:belongsToCentury a rdf:Property .
ex:hasTheme a rdf:Property .
ex:content a rdf:Property .